headline: The Allstate Corporation (ALL) Hits Fresh High: Is There Still Room to Run?

headline: Travelers Recognized for Military-Friendly Culture
summary: HARTFORD, Conn., November 24, 2025--The Travelers Companies, Inc. (NYSE: TRV) today announced it has maintained its Gold rank on VIQTORY’s Military Friendly® Companies list, as well as its inclusion on the Military Friendly® Employers and Military Spouse Friendly Employers® lists. The company was also once again named to the Military Times Best for Vets Employers list.
